reviewText: Very tame for a racy title. Nothing like I had expected. There are some great former playmates in it though.
It is an okay video, very late 80s-early 90s format for a 2000 show. It is a decent display of how to express intimacy to your lover though. It does not show 101 ways though.
I want this DVD  for reviewing,OK? AND THE PRICE HAS TO LESS THEN TWENTY DOLLARS.OR IF YOU HAVE ENOUGH TIME TO COPY. THANK YOU!
